paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
with cte as(
    select distinct 
        ao.subOrderId, 
        ao.orderDate, 
        ao.Channel 
    from `temp.table_a` a left join `temp.attributed_Orders` ao 
    on ao.subOrderId=a.subOrderId 
    where DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),ao.orderDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 15)
    
select distinct 
    orderDate, 
    count(distinct case when Channel = 'FB Channel' then subOrderId end) as FB_orders,
    count(distinct subOrderId) as SD_orders 
from cte 
group by orderDate
order by orderDate
",1000)
